    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お待たせー！\n結構、支度に時間掛かっちゃった～……",
      "startTime": 3.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "って、わわ！？　芽衣が一杯いるよ！？\n何これ、どういうことー！？",
      "startTime": 10.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（マズい……また芽衣が一人増えたぞ……）\n（これ以上は本当に頭がパンクしてしまう……）",
      "startTime": 17.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "あ……もしかしなくてもこの時間の芽衣！？\nた、たたた、大変だ、これってこれって……！",
      "startTime": 26.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei004_3.m4a",
      "text": "禁則事項だーーーー！",
      "startTime": 30.6307481447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "どうした？　今更一人増えただけだろう……？\n何をそんなに慌てているんだ？",
      "startTime": 38.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "だってこんなこと昨日はなかった！\nどうしよどうしよ！　タイムパイナップルだーーーー！",
      "startTime": 44.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "未来の未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "それを言うならパンナコッタじゃなかった！？\nあれれ？　パンダ動物園だっけ……？",
      "startTime": 52.3333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "遠い未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "と、とにかくこうなったら時間を戻すしかないよ！\nこのままだとえっと、えーっとすっごく大変だもん！",
      "startTime": 60.1333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "遥か未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "ダメダメ！　そんなことしたら時間逆流で次元断層の\nそれこそ猫ちゃんハリケーンだよー！！",
      "startTime": 72.1333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "禁則事項に禁則事項で禁則事項のパタパタエビフライ！\nそれってやっぱりタイムパイナップルだよーーーー！",
      "startTime": 80.9333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇねぇ、芽衣達何言ってるのかな？\nすっごく楽しそうだし、芽衣も混ざりたい！",
      "startTime": 89.5999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "やめておけ、多分それどころじゃない……\nというか事態が悪化しそうだ……",
      "startTime": 95.6999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "しかしええと、タイムパイナップルか……\nもしかしてタイムパラドックスのことか？",
      "startTime": 103.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "あ、それみくるちゃんから聞いたことあるよ！\n確か未来と現在が変わっちゃうー的なやつ！",
      "startTime": 110.9666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei2",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei012_3.m4a",
      "text": "多分それだーーーー！\nとりあえずなんとかしなきゃ！　えーーーーい！",
      "startTime": 117.7999992371,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_teleportation-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2966.666666700007,
          "startTime": 120.7666659038
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_teleportation-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4666.66666670001,
          "startTime": 122.4666659038
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_teleportation-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6100.000000000008,
          "startTime": 123.8999992371
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_teleportation-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7633.334096200002,
          "startTime": 125.4333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_teleportation-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9100.00000000001,
          "startTime": 126.8999992371
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "わわ、芽衣達がぴかぴかに光ってる！\n宝石みたいで綺麗だねー",
      "startTime": 125.8333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "い、言ってる場合か！？\nぐっ、目が開けていられない……！！",
      "startTime": 130.8666659038,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_teleportation-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2440.9982287000103,
          "startTime": 130.9666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_teleportation-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 128.525668438
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "うおっ！？　はぁ……はぁ……！？\nなんだ、さっきのは……夢、だったのか……？",
      "startTime": 139.5333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "でも妙にリアルだったし、芽衣達にもみくちゃに\nされたあとが服に残っている……まさか……？",
      "startTime": 148.3333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "あー、やっぱりごろーんって寝っ転がってたんだー\nぐっすりだったんだね、スーツがしわくちゃだよ～",
      "startTime": 157.5999992371,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 104.41939849999926,
          "startTime": 153.4999992371
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣が直してあげるよー、今からドーナツ\n買いに行くんだから、綺麗にしなくちゃね",
      "startTime": 164.2251262266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、ありがとう……はぁ……\nついでに水もくれると助かるんだが……",
      "startTime": 171.6999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、はい、どうぞー。ふふ、でもめずらしいね\nいつもなら距離が近いーって断るのに",
      "startTime": 181.8999992371,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cup-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2185.576002000005,
          "startTime": 177.0999992371
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　あっ、す、すまない……\nその……余裕がなくてな……",
      "startTime": 188.5333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "なぁ、芽衣……\n未来人についてもう一度聞かせてくれないか？",
      "startTime": 194.1666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "みくるちゃんの話だよね？　普段のみくるちゃんは\nちょっぴり泣き虫だけど、とっても優しくてねー",
      "startTime": 204.281228301,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "それでね、SOS団のマスコットキャラなの\nみんなに愛されてて芽衣も大好きになっちゃった",
      "startTime": 212.358837006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "それとみくるちゃんには未来の姿もあって……\nとーっても綺麗で素敵なんだって！",
      "startTime": 221.2744932155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei020.m4a",
      "text": "禁則事項で禁則事項して未来から来てるみたいで\n結局禁則事項だらけでよく分からなくて……",
      "startTime": 229.2333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-mei021.m4a",
      "text": "TPDD？　AED？　CD？　みたいな\n目に見えない何かで時空間移動してるんだって！",
      "startTime": 240.3666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "全然分からないが……物凄い技術なんだな……\nそれって光ったりするのか……？",
      "startTime": 251.0999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
